Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从窗口眺望夜空的话\N窓から空を見ていると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.69,0:00:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以看到很厉害的东西\Nとっても　すごいものを　見たんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人们都笑者说\N大人は誰も笑いながら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我电视看太多了\Nテレビの見過ぎと言うけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我绝对绝对\N僕は　絶対に絶対に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会说谎\N嘘なんか言ってない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.79,0:00:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不会用名为常识的眼镜\N常識と言う眼鏡で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.19,0:00:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我们的世界\N僕たちの世界は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.59,0:00:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行窥视\Nのぞけやしないのさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.59,0:00:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘记了梦想的\N夢を忘れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.59,0:01:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古老的地球人啊\N古い地球人よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好奇妙的感觉\N不思議な気持ち
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.93,0:01:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.15,0:01:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會成為敵人的人多半都很頑固
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.42,0:01:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由駕駛員升起來的指揮官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.07,0:01:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不乖乖坐著指揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.88,0:01:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還開出反管製品的MS出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.92,0:01:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之他被我打敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.73,0:01:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是Z高達的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.76,0:01:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我太有實力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.40,0:01:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第七話 咖扎的風暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.14,0:02:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們所在的地區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.41,0:02:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪應該是躲在這邊的廢鐵堆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.50,0:02:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確切位置尚未掌握
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.21,0:02:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以亞加瑪想出外的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.25,0:02:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定得先經過我們才能抵達港口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.12,0:02:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必再解釋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.97,0:02:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,計算亞加瑪的最短距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要用安多拉的主炮轟它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.42,0:02:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殖民地內用戰艦主炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.05,0:02:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這太過火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.93,0:03:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.21,0:03:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要讓市民知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.32,0:03:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力量就代表正義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.19,0:03:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一下,馬士文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.58,0:03:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事到如今我不聽新的提案\N潘帕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.50,0:03:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,潘帕幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.40,0:03:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不甘心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.73,0:03:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想到這樣就無法替朋友報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.51,0:03:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便心痛不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.79,0:03:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們駕駛員究竟是為何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.49,0:03:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要日夜訓練駕駛MS呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.95,0:03:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,潘帕...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.65,0:03:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我打敗Z高達的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.21,0:03:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.36,0:03:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們才是真正的騎士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.24,0:03:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人一定很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.17,0:03:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.42,0:03:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就暫時交給你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.51,0:03:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,謝謝大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.85,0:03:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.02,0:04:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪到底躲在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.11,0:04:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個小鬼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.18,0:04:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有必要去收破爛的集會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.30,0:04:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是,工業用艙口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.48,0:04:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是他們在管理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.19,0:04:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟他們解釋一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.38,0:04:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們一定會打開艙口的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.83,0:04:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趕快讓亞加瑪離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.68,0:04:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然會被敵人打壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些收破爛的會樂死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.78,0:04:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又多了好多鐵屑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.45,0:04:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.19,0:04:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前殖民地就先完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.52,0:04:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們是講不聽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.90,0:04:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些人都跟蓋蒙差不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.24,0:04:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說我什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.44,0:04:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我問你說我什麼阿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.73,0:04:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,那個...快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.82,0:04:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.98,0:04:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嗎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.76,0:05:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香格里拉的居民都在注意呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.72,0:05:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們一定要光明正大的打贏戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.78,0:05:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不會做出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.89,0:05:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有辱大人名譽的卑鄙行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.83,0:05:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,去吧\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.15,0:05:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薩克暴風部隊,出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.25,0:05:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,潘帕,比安,做出那個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.75,0:05:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.37,0:05:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文大人,我們走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比安,潘帕,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.74,0:06:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太善解人意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.44,0:06:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薩克部隊,盡量的表現吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.31,0:06:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看一下路阿,可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.97,0:06:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直待在破爛堆中有點無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪的名聲都快臭掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.55,0:06:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在埋在垃圾堆中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.69,0:06:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們都快生銹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是布拉杜艦長不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.18,0:06:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一點進步也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.70,0:06:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你的幫忙,奇馬達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.54,0:06:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.63,0:06:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,抓住他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.55,0:06:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.39,0:06:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別跑\N好痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.43,0:06:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,等一下\N不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們快來幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.68,0:06:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.99,0:07:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵襲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.62,0:07:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了慎重起見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.58,0:07:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那邊的垃圾山也要調查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.41,0:07:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,潘帕,,你去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.40,0:07:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.43,0:07:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比安,你跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.45,0:07:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人呢...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩架新型MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.60,0:07:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花,去開動Z高達去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.14,0:07:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯,你去開動密達斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.91,0:07:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我嗎?確定嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.70,0:07:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫你去開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.49,0:07:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.59,0:07:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別跑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.73,0:07:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個臭老頭...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.46,0:07:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.62,0:07:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有MS你只是普通的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.68,0:07:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的拳頭對我是沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.85,0:08:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛\N那時候我有救你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.14,0:08:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,情況不一樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.56,0:08:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准動!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.24,0:08:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要扭斷你的骨頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.46,0:08:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.07,0:08:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.46,0:08:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別檔著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.14,0:08:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達跟密達斯\N去引開敵人的注意力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.62,0:08:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之間快疏散平民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.21,0:08:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯絡到捷度嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.63,0:08:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.55,0:08:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解了,Z高達出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.89,0:08:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長,請讓我動手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.03,0:08:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,潘帕,聽著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.31,0:08:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要光明正大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.14,0:08:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.21,0:08:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會一對一決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.31,0:08:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是敵人的MS!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.39,0:09:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油,潘帕,比安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.12,0:09:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,市民在看阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.24,0:09:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.63,0:09:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷靜下來,特雷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.24,0:09:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼快就想逃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.56,0:09:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比安!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.48,0:09:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.12,0:09:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手阿,比安!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.77,0:09:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,背後攻擊是卑鄙小人阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對...是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.83,0:09:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼搞的..?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.44,0:09:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之我好像得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.04,0:09:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.46,0:09:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從背後攻擊太卑鄙了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.05,0:09:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.27,0:09:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那這樣就沒意見了吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.59,0:09:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手!會斷掉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.37,0:09:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要替肯丁報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.90,0:09:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他像我弟弟一樣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.71,0:09:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這跟我無關!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.84,0:09:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甩不掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.84,0:09:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個駕駛員!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.51,0:09:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.27,0:10:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還太嫩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香格里拉的各位市民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.77,0:10:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們現在正與亞加瑪的MS作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.57,0:10:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有絕對數量的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.51,0:10:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但卻要求做一對一的決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.82,0:10:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因為我們不想傷害殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.18,0:10:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相較之下,亞加瑪卑鄙透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.92,0:10:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們偷偷摸摸的逃進殖民地內部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.96,0:10:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全沒考慮殖民地的損害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.00,0:10:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.08,0:10:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們的戰艦不也進入殖民地裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.47,0:10:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪準備出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.73,0:10:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.19,0:10:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是那種沒臉皮的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪緊急出動!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.05,0:10:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引開敵人注意力\N支援Z高達跟密達斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.40,0:10:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加馬準備出動!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.69,0:10:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各崗位人員各就各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.79,0:10:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道用法吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.00,0:10:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以隨便讓我玩嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.17,0:10:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.30,0:10:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏不是宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.08,0:10:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是有能源調節裝置嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說有調節裝置\N在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.90,0:11:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.83,0:11:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們被迫採取非常手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.66,0:11:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,責任完全在亞加瑪身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.15,0:11:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪給所有人帶來麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.54,0:11:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就麻煩的更徹底!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.50,0:11:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.09,0:11:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請各位市民協助...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒打中阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.05,0:11:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在調節哪裏!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.76,0:11:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們想破壞殖民地嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.77,0:11:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香格里拉的各位市民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們看到剛才亞加瑪的攻擊了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是卑鄙的偷襲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.63,0:11:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕對不會原諒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.06,0:11:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算會毀掉整各殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.93,0:11:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要戰鬥到底!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.55,0:11:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們要恨就恨亞加瑪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.54,0:12:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開捷度阿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.43,0:12:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在看哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.68,0:12:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道我的厲害嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.73,0:12:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.25,0:12:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好重,好重阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.17,0:12:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.34,0:12:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.82,0:12:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.01,0:12:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是本地人吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.72,0:12:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道亞加瑪躲在哪裏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何只知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.20,0:12:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就帶我去亞加瑪吧\N當作回報我的救命之恩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.08,0:13:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不是帶路的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.39,0:13:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在很忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.33,0:13:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你叫什麼名子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.50,0:13:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是拉比安羅茲的露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.39,0:13:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉比安羅茲的露卡...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.23,0:13:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是橋,別掉下去阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.64,0:13:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些孩子到哪裏去了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.04,0:13:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.28,0:13:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才發光的地方可能有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.10,0:13:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?剛才的小飛機是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.94,0:13:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是在這一帶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.87,0:14:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.40,0:14:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭\N那是Z高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.21,0:14:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼我第一眼看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.36,0:14:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達會這麼慘?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.24,0:14:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.36,0:14:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是援軍嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.69,0:14:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新的追兵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.87,0:14:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的戰鬥機是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.39,0:14:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不用正當攻法了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.26,0:14:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,覺悟吧,Z高達!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.18,0:14:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放手,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.49,0:14:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.24,0:14:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的腳...糟了\N踩不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.99,0:14:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛員還沒死?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.40,0:14:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.52,0:14:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來引開敵人,你快逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.35,0:14:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.53,0:14:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.50,0:14:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.87,0:14:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的戰機是...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.36,0:14:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪的援軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.84,0:15:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必管那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.55,0:15:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重要的是Z高達,到底躲到哪裏了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.31,0:15:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.99,0:15:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長,其實我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.08,0:15:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那戰鬥機是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.34,0:15:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達,你干麻像木頭\N一樣站著不動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.17,0:15:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你完了,Z高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.30,0:15:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花,幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.75,0:15:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊,過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.38,0:15:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼車子...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.06,0:15:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衝過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.35,0:15:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.43,0:15:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.59,0:15:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.35,0:15:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來換班,你得請我吃一頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.43,0:15:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.52,0:15:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.07,0:15:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.04,0:15:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.31,0:15:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?那也是敵人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.13,0:16:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像在跟敵人的MS交手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.17,0:16:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達,聽見了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.19,0:16:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一架由我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.39,0:16:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一架給你應付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是拉比安羅茲的露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.45,0:16:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的...你沒有問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.22,0:16:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包在我身上!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.37,0:16:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這邊是Z高達\N小心別受到波及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.35,0:16:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為在殖民地內部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.90,0:16:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就可以胡作非為嗎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.80,0:16:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.34,0:16:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地層下陷了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.49,0:16:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確定那是核戰機嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.11,0:16:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,是從拉比安羅茲飛來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.40,0:16:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫個炮座支援核戰機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.73,0:16:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.74,0:16:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核戰機!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請到亞加碼的射程內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.66,0:16:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.52,0:16:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能源調整完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.36,0:16:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太弱就沒意義了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.02,0:16:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.00,0:16:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.59,0:17:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打中了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.04,0:17:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打中了,真痛快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.66,0:17:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,疑!逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.04,0:17:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的Z高達!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.14,0:17:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不出來,我就逼你出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.48,0:17:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殖民地被開了個洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.31,0:17:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定有彌補的機關...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.29,0:17:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是在這裏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.52,0:17:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,按錯了...這是機關炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.59,0:17:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.96,0:17:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次在受到攻擊\N殖民地一定會被打個大洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.98,0:17:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.12,0:17:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會在容忍你們放肆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.77,0:17:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來了嗎?比安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.54,0:18:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,潘帕,使用煙霧模式\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.51,0:18:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.68,0:18:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是為了大氣層內的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.00,0:18:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而專門研發出的戰法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.32,0:18:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在煙霧中\N你就施展不出手腳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.18,0:18:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是,隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.67,0:18:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要如何分辨敵人的位置?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.54,0:18:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人的米諾夫斯基粒子\N已經破壞了雷達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.99,0:18:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照計算\N煙霧應該只會蓋住我們的機身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.52,0:18:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煙霧擴散的比預計的快!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.25,0:18:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雙方條件都一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.84,0:18:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我方數目還比較多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.77,0:18:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨便打吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.38,0:18:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總有一顆會中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.31,0:18:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.94,0:18:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亂七八糟...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.67,0:18:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去,殖民地會毀滅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.31,0:19:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼煙霧..?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.17,0:19:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達,你沒事吧...!\NZ高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.03,0:19:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問題可大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.46,0:19:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照這樣下去,殖民地會毀滅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.59,0:19:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別用無線電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.78,0:19:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會被發現位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.21,0:19:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個煙霧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.38,0:19:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不消除煙霧就很難瞄準...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.51,0:19:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煙霧是因為空氣而擴散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.51,0:19:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.85,0:19:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別太過分!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.78,0:19:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.02,0:19:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香格里拉!\N對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.60,0:19:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煙霧...怎麼不見了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.25,0:19:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這裏!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.19,0:20:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!你竟敢傷害比安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.25,0:20:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也一樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.32,0:20:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險!\N注意後方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.58,0:20:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.08,0:20:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文大人...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.66,0:20:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薩克部隊竟然全滅...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.76,0:20:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.33,0:20:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,取消出航命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.09,0:20:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們對Z高達還研究不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.43,0:21:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緊急措施做好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.49,0:21:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的交給殖民地公署
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.46,0:21:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回亞加碼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.35,0:21:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下,露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.10,0:21:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉比安羅茲是修理船的船屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.70,0:21:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.66,0:21:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉度艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.32,0:21:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉比安羅茲在等亞加碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.65,0:21:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你來的好,我等了很久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.67,0:21:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.96,0:21:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能不能想辦法打開工業用艙口?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.73,0:21:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不能久留了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.92,0:21:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人馬上就會攻過來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.30,0:21:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.07,0:21:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了,我試試吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.98,0:22:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然照這樣下去\N殖民地真的會被破壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.89,0:22:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家走吧,莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.99,0:22:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是\N我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.13,0:22:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等,我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.15,0:22:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是開核戰機進來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.04,0:22:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼說你有好方法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.85,0:22:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.07,0:22:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核戰機跟亞加碼的大小差太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.45,0:22:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被我痛打一頓的大叔還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.78,0:22:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人是殺也殺不死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.10,0:22:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在没有道路的荒野里\N道もない荒れた原野に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.10,0:22:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建造铁路真是一件辛苦差事\Nレールを作るのは苦しいことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.10,0:23:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\Nだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.50,0:23:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以不知晓远方\N遠い向こうも知らなくちゃいけない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.70,0:23:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我们的路现在才开始\N僕達は これからなんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.80,0:23:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们都说我们是“忘记了梦想的小孩子”\N“夢を忘れた子供達”と 人は言う
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.50,0:23:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊啊 时代正在哭泣\Nああー 時代が泣いている
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.99,0:23:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘恩負義人到處都有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.39,0:23:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逸扎原本可是我們救上來的人耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.75,0:23:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是這次他卻用兩台蓋傑攻過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.08,0:23:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊Z卻不聽使喚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.57,0:23:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 給我好好地行動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.20,0:24:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是NEWTYPE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.95,0:24:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這麼武斷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.09,0:24:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集 高達ZZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.27,0:24:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二度敲響鎮魂的鐘聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.82,0:24:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太帥了

